        <h1>Equality</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"><img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/likestilling_150x113.jpg" alt="Men and women talking together" title="Men and women talking together" /></div>
        
            <img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/likestilling_150x113.jpg" alt="Men and women talking together" title="Men and women talking together" class="temaIngressImg" />
        <div class="descriptionText"><div>
	<p><em>The Ministry of Children and Equality</em> is responsible for coordinating the Government’s family and equality policies and legislation in this area. <em>The Ministry of Labour and Social Inclusion</em> is responsible for immigration and asylum policy. <em>The&nbsp;Ministry of Local Government and Modernisation</em>&nbsp;is responsible for the policy towards the Sami people and minorities.<br />&nbsp;<br />On this page you will find general information and documents that relate to equality. You can explore this topic in more detail by using the menu on the right.</p>
</div></div>
